To open any directory or file 
dir 
To change to any directory
cd name of the directory
To make a directroy
mkdir and name the directory
To remove directory or file 
rmdir space name of the directory or file
To see all hidden file and directory 
dir /a

If thedirectory is not empty and you want to delete it or remove it 
rmdir /s and choose Y
If you want to go to the starting point of you command 
press Home 

